org.jivesoftware.smack.packet

Interface Element

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtensionElement, NamedElement, Packet, PacketExtension, PlainStreamElement, TopLevelStreamElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bind, Bind.Feature, Compress, Compress.Feature, Compressed, DefaultExtensionElement, EmptyResultIQ, ErrorIQ, FullStreamElement, IQ, Mechanisms, Message, Presence, SaslStreamElements.AuthMechanism, SaslStreamElements.Challenge, SaslStreamElements.Response, SaslStreamElements.SASLFailure, SaslStreamElements.Success, Session, Session.Feature, SimpleIQ, Stanza, StartTls, StreamError, StreamOpen, UnparsedIQ

    public interface Element
    Interface to represent a XML element. This is similar to ExtensionElement, but does not carry a namespace and is usually included as child element of an stanza(/packet) extension.
